Package io.github.msdk.featuredetection.adap3d.algorithms

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ADAP3DPeakDetectionAlgorithm
    ADAP3DPeakDetectionAlgorithm class.
    ADAP3DPeakDetectionAlgorithm.GoodPeakInfo
    GoodPeakInfo class is used to save information of good peaks.
    BiGaussian
    BiGaussian Class is used for fitting BiGaussian on EIC.
    BiGaussianSimilarityTest
    BiGaussianSimilarityTest class is used for determining true or false peak by comparing BiGaussian values with intensity values of given m/z and left and right bounds (variables leftBound and rightBound).
    ContinuousWaveletTransform
    ContinuousWaveletTransform class.
    ContinuousWaveletTransform.DataPoint
    This is the data model for creating data points for CWT
    CurveTool
    CurveTool class is used for estimation of Full width half maximum.
    FeatureTools
    FeatureTools class.
    Math
    This class contains mathematical functions
    Peak3DTest
    Peak3DTest is used for determining true or false peak by comparing adjacent m/z-slices in profile data.
    Peak3DTest.Result
    Result class is used for returning lower and upper mz bound,boolean good peak value and list of similarity value.
    SignalToNoise
    SignalToNoise class.
    SliceSparseMatrix
    SliceSparseMatrix class is used for slicing the sparse matrix of raw data as per given mz value.
    SliceSparseMatrix.Triplet
    Triplet is used for representing elements of sparse matrix.
    SliceSparseMatrix.VerticalSliceDataPoint
    This is the data model for getting vertical slice from sparse matrix.
    SortAndKeepOriginalIndecies
    SortAndKeepOriginalIndecies class.
